<span id="freeTextContainer10583003152465038227">These stories - about Yunior and his family in the Dominican Republic and New Jersey are so, so good. In a shattering, explosive way. Now that I&apos;ve read his three books, I just hope Diaz publishes another novel or short story collection soon.</span>
  <span id="freeText10583003152465038227" style="display:none">These stories - about Yunior and his family in the Dominican Republic and New Jersey are so, so good. In a shattering, explosive way. Now that I've read his three books, I just hope Diaz publishes another novel or short story collection soon.</span>
